INSERT INTO `email_messages` (`id`, `name`, `message`) VALUES
(1, 'welcome', 'Dear $firstName$,\r\n\r\nYour personal information has now been entered into the Christchurch Tramp Club database. Welcome to the CTC!\r\n\r\nYour username on the club website is: $loginName$\r\nYour newly created password is: $pass$\r\n\r\nYou will probably want to change your password to something more easily remembered. Just log in to the club website ( www.ctc.org.nz ) using the above username and password, and select the \'User Details\' entry from the \'Members\' menu on the left.\r\n\r\nYour other personal details are shown below. Please check to make sure everything\'s right. If you find any errors you can either correct them yourself via the club website or reply to this email giving any corrections. \r\n\r\nThe club website, www.ctc.org.nz, can be consulted at any time for up-to-date information on trips and social events and to read recent trip reports. When logged into the site you are able to:\r\n\r\n - sign up for upcoming trips\r\n - update your personal profile (username, password, address, phone etc)\r\n - view contact details for trip leaders\r\n - get a list of all members and their contact details\r\n - view the newsletter archive and other club documents\r\n - post trip reports\r\n\r\nIMPORTANT - To ensure you get emails about trips that you have signed up for, please add noreply@ctc.org.nz to your email address book or spam-filter whitelist (please email webmaster@ctc.org.nz if you need help doing this).\r\n\r\nYour personal details in our database are as follows:\r\n\r\n============================\r\n\r\nFirst name: $firstName$\r\nLast name: $lastName$\r\nEmail: $primaryEmail$\r\nHome phone: $homePhone$\r\nAddress:\r\n     $address1$\r\n     $address2$\r\n     $city$ $postcode$\r\n\r\nReceive mailed newsletter? $mailNewsletterBool$\r\nOn club email list? $onEmailListBool$\r\n\r\n============================\r\n\r\nMany thanks for joining. We hope you enjoy our club.\r\n\r\n-- The Website Team');
